headline: MetLife CEO and CFO to Speak at Bank of America Securities 2026 Financial Services Conference
summary: NEW YORK, January 29, 2026--MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET) today announced that Michel Khalaf, president and CEO, and John McCallion, executive vice president and CFO, and head of MetLife Investment Management, will participate in a fireside chat at the Bank of America Securities 2026 Financial Services Conference on Tuesday, Feb. 10, 2026, beginning at 9:40 a.m. (ET).
